        "text": "Mr. Hoove\nF.B.I. O Flying Discs\nDear Sir: They say that if\nwe are crazy we are the last\nto know. If that may be my\ncase but I hope not. You know a\nabout 2 months ago, a number\nof people said they saw flying\ndiscs, and the papers admit"
      },
